00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:48,020
 I was sharing about this camp I was at.

662
00:31:48,020 --> 00:31:52,260
 It was this really religious, boring camp as a kid, a music camp.

663
00:31:52,260 --> 00:31:54,580
 It was literally, it was you snooze, you win.

664
00:31:54,580 --> 00:31:56,460
 That's what I called it.

665
00:31:56,460 --> 00:31:57,460
 And I was there.

666
00:31:57,460 --> 00:31:58,460
 They invited me to come.

667
00:31:58,460 --> 00:31:59,460
 It was like the Bible teacher.

