00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:53,260
 Who is this guy?

706
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:56,900
 Holy.

707
00:33:56,900 --> 00:33:58,900
 Who is this guy?

708
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:01,420
 Oh, this?

709
00:34:01,420 --> 00:34:02,820
 This?

710
00:34:02,820 --> 00:34:04,020
 This?"

